{"tid":2014272,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【又要印錢】美國眾議院民主黨提出新一輪30,000億美元疫症紓困法案","createTime":"2020-05-13T02:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T12:24:58.000Z","uid":351009,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f1049da3e0b405187c052bb8a1cc738021589e","tid":2014272,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:30:04.000Z","msg":"民主黨5月12號提出長達1,800頁嘅新一輪紓困法案，預計星期五表決<br />\n議長佩洛西: &quot;Although it's a big ticket, it's a big problem&quot;<br />\n眾議院現時由民主黨佔大多數<br />\n<br />\n法案建議用30,000億美元作紓困措施，內容包括:<br />\n&bull; 提供10,000億經濟援助俾地方同州政府<br />\n&bull; 第二輪全民 $1,200派錢方案，家庭上限為$6,000美元<br />\n&bull; 提供2,000億高危津貼俾essential worker<br />\n&bull; 提供750億用作病毒測試同contact tracing<br />\n&bull; 延長每星期 $600聯邦失業救濟金到2021年一月份<br />\n&bull; 1,750億租金、按揭、水電煤補助<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他，有興趣click入link睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/12/coronavirus-updates-house-democrats-unveil-3-trillion-relief-bill.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2Fcoronavirus-updates-house-democrats-unveil-3-trillion-relief-bill.html&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=88f79ffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/12/coronavirus-updates-house-democrats-unveil-3-trillion-relief-bill.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/12/nancy-pelosi-3-trillion-coronavirus-bill-is-a-big-ticket-for-big-problem.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2Fnancy-pelosi-3-trillion-coronavirus-bill-is-a-big-ticket-for-big-problem.html&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=f46f28d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/12/nancy-pelosi-3-trillion-coronavirus-bill-is-a-big-ticket-for-big-problem.html</a>"},{"pid":"11bbde944d107f47c23805f854f0fb35f503e71b","tid":2014272,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T02:32:39.000Z"